info.headline: High Wind Warning issued September 23 at 4:30AM EDT until September 23 at 6:00PM EDT by NWS Philadelphia - Mount Holly
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 PM EDT THIS EVENING... * WHAT...Northeast winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts of 50 to 60 mph. * WHERE...In Delaware, Delaware Beaches. In New Jersey, Atlantic Coastal Cape May, Coastal Atlantic and Coastal Ocean. * WHEN...Until 6 PM EDT this evening. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds will blow down trees and power lines. Widespread power outages are expected. Travel will be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
info.instruction: People should avoid being outside around trees. Use caution if you must drive.
